->Database is a organized collection of data
->DBMS is a software that manages the database and interacts with endusers, applications.
  It(DBMS) is like piece of software that enables users to interact with database.
->MongoDB
  collection(eg like table)
  document(eg like rows)
  fields(eg like columns)
  ->It has flexible schema
  ->MAQ -Mongo Query Language
  ->Easy to scale horizantally & vertically, but where as RDMS tough to scale horizantally
  ->Real Time, Big Data, Distributed computing 


  





